## Artefact [/artefacts/{artefact_uuid}]

An Image object has the following attributes:

+ uuid
+ created_at - An ISO8601 date when the image was published.
+ updated_at - An ISO8601 date when the image was last updated.
+ url
+ images - An array of assigned images, if any.

+ Parameters
    + artefact_uuid (required, uuid, `eddfa2ae-7cfe-441a-ac7b-eda912e3d867`) ... UUID of the Image in form of a string

